Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.39,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}始まりはZERO　終わりならZET
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.39,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}起點是ZERO 終點是ZET
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.98,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}疼くその手を 空にかざせ
